               <msContents>
                  <summary>Papyrus private letter from Egypt from Iohannes to Apa Daniel, both monks. Iohannes requests that Apa Daniel, whom Iohannes addresses as father, let someone bring something to him in a monastery. Includes greetings to Apa David and others</summary>
